source.query:
COPY INTO "MYVOYAGE_CLEANSED"."RS_OMNI_VIPS_DAILY_PART_HEADER_CLN_BASELINE"( "WS_EXT_PH_PLAN_NUM","WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM","WS_EXT_PH_NAME","WS_EXT_PH_PART_DIV_SUB","WS_EXT_PH_BRTH_DATE","WS_EXT_PH_PLENT_DATE",
"WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L1","WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L2","WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L3","WS_EXT_PH_CITY","WS_EXT_PH_STATE","WS_EXT_PH_ZIP","WS_EXT_PH_STAT",
"WS_EXT_PH_TERM_DATE","WS_EXT_PH_LAST_CNTRB_DATE","WS_EXT_PH_STAT_REASON","WS_EXT_PH_LOC_TAX_CODE","WS_EXT_PH_ALT_STATE",
"WS_EXT_PH_FIRST_CNTRB_DATE","WS_EXT_PH_ATTAINED_AGE","WS_EXT_PH_PF999_BAL","WS_EXT_PH_PA999_BAL","WS_EXT_PH_ADV_ACCT_IND","WS_EXT_PH_OMNI_VERSION","WS_EXT_PH_VRR_PL_STATUS","WS_EXT_PH_VRR_PL_TERM","WS_EXT_PH_CONV_PL_NUM","WS_EXT_PH_CLIENT_ID","WS_EXT_PH_SUB_CLIENT_ID",
"WS_EXT_PH_SSO_CLIENT_ID","WS_EXT_PH_CLIENT_STATUS","SWFDL_LOAD_ID","SWFDL_CREATED_BY","SWFDL_CREATED_TS","SWFDL_UPDATED_BY","SWFDL_UPDATED_TS") FROM (SELECT 
TRIM(CAST($1    AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_PART_NUM    AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_NAME    AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_PART_DIV_SUB    AS VARCHAR(255))),
CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(WS_EXT_PH_BRTH_DATE ),2,8) AS NUMBER(38,0)),
CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(WS_EXT_PH_PLENT_DATE ),2,8) AS NUMBER(38,0)),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L1  AS VARCHAR(255))  ),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L2  AS VARCHAR(255))  ),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_ADDR_L3  AS VARCHAR(255))  ),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_CITY              AS VARCHAR(255))  ),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_STATE              AS VARCHAR(255))  ),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_ZIP              AS VARCHAR(255))  ),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_STAT            AS NUMBER(38,0))),
CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(WS_EXT_PH_TERM_DATE ),2,8) AS NUMBER(38,0)),
CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(WS_EXT_PH_LAST_CNTRB_DATE ),2,8) AS NUMBER(38,0)),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_STAT_REASON            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_LOC_TAX_CODE            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_ALT_STATE            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_FIRST_CNTRB_DATE AS NUMBER(38,0))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_ATTAINED_AGE            AS NUMBER(38,5))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_PF999_BAL            AS NUMBER(38,5))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_PA999_BAL            AS NUMBER(38,5))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_ADV_ACCT_IND            AS NUMBER(38,0))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_OMNI_VERSION            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_VRR_PL_STATUS            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_VRR_PL_TERM            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_CONV_PL_NUM            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_CLIENT_ID            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_SUB_CLIENT_ID            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_SSO_CLIENT_ID            AS VARCHAR(255))),
TRIM(CAST(WS_EXT_PH_CLIENT_STATUS            AS VARCHAR(255))),
SWFDL_LOAD_ID	,
SWFDL_CREATED_BY	,
SWFDL_CREATED_TS	,
SWFDL_UPDATED_BY	,
SWFDL_UPDATED_TS
FROM "MYVOYAGE_UNIT"."MYVOYAGE_STAGE"."RS_OMNI_VIPS_DAILY_PART_HEADER_STG_BASELINE_MASKING")
